            "created_at": "2015-10-13T18:48:33Z",
            "updated_at": "2015-10-13T18:48:33Z",
            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "While I do see the use for configuration via environment variables I have doubts about the json serialization.\n\nI wonder whether typing (part of) app.config similar to click options would be beneficial and then support:\n- http://click.pocoo.org/5/options/#values-from-environment-variables\n- http://click.pocoo.org/5/options/#multiple-values-from-environment-values\n- http://click.pocoo.org/5/commands/#overriding-defaults\n\nAn app's config would have default values, could be overridden by config file, provided by envionment variables and via cli parameters.\n\nThis might be in line with the new [flask cli](http://flask.pocoo.org/docs/dev/cli/#command-line-interface)\n"
        },
